{"tid":276443,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"FE Heroes 火焰之紋章（17）送嗰隻5星冇技ON99","createTime":"2017-06-08T21:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T01:39:42.000Z","uid":13100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"414efbdb8d9c46997380539280186cc3c986fe5d","tid":276443,"uid":13100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T21:38:42.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">新Post Template:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1wkveQBRYrdlRzxQdiAi-zS7jw5nhKnxMcf9oleTMsdY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1wkveQBRYrdlRzxQdiAi-zS7jw5nhKnxMcf9oleTMsdY%2F&d=ayWF0Xl6EeUFaLntekyQBpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=f02b1a3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1wkveQBRYrdlRzxQdiAi-zS7jw5nhKnxMcf9oleTMsdY/</a><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C2fXORaUoAEovwu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC2fXORaUoAEovwu.jpg&h=557d625c&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\nPV: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cCtFNO9ULdc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcCtFNO9ULdc&d=ayWF0Xl6EeUFaLntekyQBpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=c662390e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cCtFNO9ULdc</a><br />\n <br />\n官網: <a href=\"https://fire-emblem-heroes.com/ja/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffire-emblem-heroes.com%2Fja%2F&d=ayWF0Xl6EeUFaLntekyQBpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=4c9c4fe9\" target=\"_blank\">https://fire-emblem-heroes.com/ja/</a><br />\n系統: <a href=\"https://fire-emblem-heroes.com/ja/system/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffire-emblem-heroes.com%2Fja%2Fsystem%2F&d=ayWF0Xl6EeUFaLntekyQBpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=989728a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://fire-emblem-heroes.com/ja/system/</a><br />\n官方Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/FE_Heroes_JP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFE_Heroes_JP&d=ayWF0Xl6EeUFaLntekyQBpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=5e6a878f\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/FE_Heroes_JP</a><br />\n <br />\n部份參戰角色:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fjaMV1RwR_8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfjaMV1RwR_8&d=ayWF0Xl6EeUFaLntekyQBpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=1540265b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fjaMV1RwR_8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dcUN53lWbA4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdcUN53lWbA4&d=ayWF0Xl6EeUFaLntekyQBpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=34140f7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dcUN53lWbA4</a><br />\n <br />\n攻略WIKI:<br />\n<a href=\"http://altema.jp/fe-heroes/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Faltema.jp%2Ffe-heroes%2F&d=ayWF0Xl6EeUFaLntekyQBpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=e9ce43d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://altema.jp/fe-heroes/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://fe-heroes.gamerch.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffe-heroes.gamerch.com%2F&d=ayWF0Xl6EeUFaLntekyQBpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=2653e10b\" target=\"_blank\">https://fe-heroes.gamerch.com/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://appmedia.jp/fe-heroes-wiki\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fappmedia.jp%2Ffe-heroes-wiki&d=ayWF0Xl6EeUFaLntekyQBpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=ddd6cd27\" target=\"_blank\">http://appmedia.jp/fe-heroes-wiki</a><br />\n <br />\n此GAME因為全球同SER<br />\n所以會到香港時間<span style=\"color: red;\">每日下午3點</span>先拎到Login Bonus同回復對戰權<br />\n <br />\n<strong>改名改語言:<br />\n去FAQ改<br />\n勳章獲得方法:</strong><br />\n修練之塔1-5/F<br />\n<strong>大勳章獲得方法:</strong><br />\n修練之塔6-10/F<br />\n<strong>英雄之翼獲得方法:</strong><br />\n打鬥技場取得<br />\n每日去搵主頁有心心嘅角色講野拎到5條<br />\n好友list打招呼拎到5條<br />\n好友list有5人以上時打招呼送多5條<br />\n賣角色:<br />\n1星5條<br />\n2星10條<br />\n3星150條<br />\n4星300條<br />\n5星1000條<br />\n <br />\n鬥技場:<br />\n每次要用一點對戰權<br />\n可挑戰其他玩家隊伍<br />\n對戰權每日三點回滿一次<br />\n會定期結算積分派英雄之翼<br />\n------------------------------------------<br />\n戰鬥系統:<br />\n同原作相比大同小異<br />\n本作冇命中率閃避率<br />\n等級高過對手5lv.時唔會有經驗值<br />\n攻方速度比守方大於5時可以發動追擊<br />\n <br />\n兵種:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8r2ts8E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8r2ts8E.png&h=350736b9&s={SIZE}\" />步行系 可行2格 可走入樹林,行1格<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nYe7i0H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnYe7i0H.png&h=a9612841&s={SIZE}\" />重裝系 可行1格 守備值較高<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bm3927a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbm3927a.png&h=06c88334&s={SIZE}\" />騎馬系 可行3格 入唔到樹林<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3O0f3c0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3O0f3c0.png&h=aac6246f&s={SIZE}\" />飛行系 可行2格 會被弓剋制 可飛過樹林,山同河<br />\n <br />\n兵器:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span>屬(劍/魔法/石)<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">綠</span>屬(斧/魔法/石)<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span>屬(槍/魔法/石)<br />\n無屬(弓/暗器/杖)<br />\n<br />\n相剋:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span>&gt;<span style=\"color: green;\">綠</span>&gt;<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span>&gt;<span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span><br />\n另外部份角色持有剋制個別兵種嘅武器<br />\n例如剋重裝系嘅劍/槌(斧), 對暗器發動追擊嘅弓, 對龍系特效嘅ファルシオン(Falchion)同封印之劍(Binding Blade)etc.<br />\n <br />\n個體修正/ 成長值:<br />\n就算係相同既角色, 都會有唔同既個體修正, 但係每個相同角色既成長比例都會係一樣, 升級時能力值提升並非隨機。<br />\n個體修正只有三個可能性:<br />\n1. 提升兩項能力, 減低兩項能力, 一項能力正常<br />\n2. 提升一項能力, 減低一項能力, 三項能力正常<br />\n3. 全部能力都正常<br />\n以チキ(紋章)為例, 等級一的能力為HP15, 攻21, 速4, 守8, 魔防6<br />\n我地比對數據就知道, チキ(紋章)既個體修正係加攻擊減魔防, 升到40級既能力一定係HP41, 攻49, 速30, 守32, 魔防25<br />\n關於各角色既個體修正, 可以查呢個網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://fireemblem.gamewith.jp/article/show/51352\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffireemblem.gamewith.jp%2Farticle%2Fshow%2F51352&d=ayWF0Xl6EeUFaLntekyQBpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=2724de8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://fireemblem.gamewith.jp/article/show/51352</a><br />\n-----------------------------------------------"},{"pid":"a715268a8a406216c3cc79782d199cf41480961f","tid":276443,"uid":95515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T00:56:21.000Z","msg":"用黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95adea15ed1a925462ad60b4b4aef52f4aa53406","tid":276443,"uid":95515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T01:39:00.000Z","msg":"[img]<a href=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/09/093752_b73b079945d13a2d7e3728e790cc9121.jpg[/img］終於打得完\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F09%2F093752_b73b079945d13a2d7e3728e790cc9121.jpg%5B%2Fimg%EF%BC%BD%E7%B5%82%E6%96%BC%E6%89%93%E5%BE%97%E5%AE%8C&d=ayWF0Xl6EeUFaLntekyQBpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=857c98b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/09/093752_b73b079945d13a2d7e3728e790cc9121.jpg[/img］終於打得完</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c166a611107319e2322a0fe5a62c18a29684a4","tid":276443,"uid":95515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T01:39:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[img][url]<a href=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/09/093752_b73b079945d13a2d7e3728e790cc9121.jpg[/img[/url]］終於打得完\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F09%2F093752_b73b079945d13a2d7e3728e790cc9121.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5B%2Furl%5D%EF%BC%BD%E7%B5%82%E6%96%BC%E6%89%93%E5%BE%97%E5%AE%8C&d=ayWF0Xl6EeUFaLntekyQBpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=46637bfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/09/093752_b73b079945d13a2d7e3728e790cc9121.jpg[/img[/url]］終於打得完</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice